org.oasis.openc2.lycan.utilities

Class Keys

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.oasis.openc2.lycan.utilities.Keys

  • public class Keys
extends java.lang.Object
    The Keys class contains a list of static strings that are used to set the key portion of key/value pairs that are pushed to the various sections of OpenC2 message. This is done so if values change for given keys as the spec matures, only need to change one class.
